Name: Zoning, Western Rail Yard Mapping Action, Manhattan (C 250024 MMM)
Title: Application No. C 250024 MMM (Western Rail Yard Mapping Action) submitted by WRY Tenant LLC pursuant to Sections 197-c and 199 of the New York City Charter for an amendment to the City Map involving: the change of grades on West 33rd Street between Eleventh Avenue and Twelfth Avenue and the delineation of public access easement, including authorization for any acquisition or disposition of real property related thereto, in accordance with Map No. ACC. 30276 dated November 8, 2024 and signed by the Borough President, Borough of Manhattan, Community District 4, Council District 3.

History.Description: This Land Use Application was Introduced by Council
This Land Use Application was Referred to Comm by Council to the Committee on Land Use
This Land Use Application was Referred to Comm by Council to the Subcommittee on Zoning and Franchises
